"CycleStreets: Suurbritannia jalgrattamarsruudid cyclestreets.net-i vahendusel"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Gosmore: An offline router that also serves as the backend for the Yours "
