msgstr ""
"Monav: võrguväline marsruudiprogramm, mis on väga kiire isegi väga mahukate "
"marsruutide arvestamisel."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"OSRM: An online router that is very fast even when calculating very large "
"routes"
msgstr ""
"OSRM: võrgumarsruudiprogramm, mis on väga kiire isegi väga mahukate "
"marsruutide arvestamisel."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"OpenRouteService: An online router that also generates driving instructions, "
